Q. Print the first -ve value found in each window of size 'k'. Print 0 if no negative in any of the sliding windows.
e.g.: {1, -2, 3, 7, 11, 17, 4, 5, -6}, k = 3. There are 3 windows, so should print:
O/P: -2, 0, -6

Ans: For space optimized solution, use below gfg's link's last solution. Otherwise Aditya Verma's youtube playlist:

